# HNG Stage 1 - Profile Intelligence Service

A REST API that enriches names using Genderize, Agify, and Nationalize APIs and stores the results in MongoDB.

## Endpoints

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | /api/profiles | Create a profile |
| GET | /api/profiles | List all profiles (filterable) |
| GET | /api/profiles/:id | Get a profile by ID |
| DELETE | /api/profiles/:id | Delete a profile |

## Example Request

```bash
POST /api/profiles
Content-Type: application/json
{ "name": "ella" }
```

## Example Response

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "id": "b3f9c1e2-7d4a-4c91-9c2a-1f0a8e5b6d12",
    "name": "ella",
    "gender": "female",
    "gender_probability": 0.99,
    "sample_size": 1234,
    "age": 46,
    "age_group": "adult",
    "country_id": "DRC",
    "country_probability": 0.85,
    "created_at": "2026-04-01T12:00:00Z"
  }
}
```

## Filtering

```
GET /api/profiles?gender=male
GET /api/profiles?country_id=NG
GET /api/profiles?age_group=adult
```

## Tech Stack

- Node.js + Express
- MongoDB Atlas
- UUID v7

## Setup

```bash
npm install
cp .env.example .env
# Add your MongoDB URI to .env
npm start
```